reviewText: Chaka is da'Bomb !!! This dvd Rocks from beginning to end ... her vocals have only improved with her years !!!! FANTASTIC FANTASTIC FANTASTIC FANTASTIC...
Great music, great artist and a great addition to my historical music collection.
Very disappointed by poor picture quality and uselessness (sticking on track 2). I gave it one star, only for quick delivery and neat packaging.
CHAKA-CHAKA KHAN IF YOU A SINGLE MAN GET THIS FOR THE LADIES THAT COME BY.
Best live DVD she ever made!
Excellent video! The clarity was exceptional well. I would recommend this to anyone that enjoy live music.

Chaka may be slowing down, but this has to be one of the best bands and backup singers she has ever sang with. The song "Through The Fire" says all that needs to be said. And the rest just enjoy......Peace

Chaka Isn't What She Use To Be But, The Band On This Gig Is Smokin!!
I'm A Musician And, I Really Enjoy Seeing A 'Good' Live Band.
